name: authentic swiss army blanket
description:
a grand statement item in your home.
stylish.
modern.
slightly industrial.

L O V E L Y

new old stock of the classic Siwiss Army military blanket.
100% wool with the iconic Swiss cross embroidered upon the red strip.

app. 60" x 80"


a wonderful addition to your life -
picnics, cuddling by the fire, camping or simply folded over your favorite chiair.

bound to be an item fought over in the household.
This is what I know about the blanket:

1. The Swiss Military manufactured these blankets from 1917 until the early 1960s. The 2 that I have listed are "new old stock" - meaning that they were never issued for use once manufactured. They are from the tail-end of manufacture.
2. Some blankets do have a stainless steel coin attached but not all were manufactured that way - these do not.
3. From my understanding, the blankets were numbered when issued, and some of the early blankets from the World War I & II era had initials for the manufacturer name and year. After World War II they stopped requiring this of their war vendors As these were never issued for use - they are blank.
4.. They are 100% wool and there are no moth holes, smells, defects or stains.


C L E A N I N G:
The blankets are 100% wool and should never be washed.
Options:
1. Dryclean
2. Hand wash in Woolite & hang dry.
3. Use drycleaning sheets in the dryer

name: vintage swiss military bread bag & bike pack
description:
Talk about style as you head to the farmers market.

A vintage Swiss bread bag whose original use was for the 
Swiss military to carry their rations in, but its modern day uses are limitless. 

It has two leather straps at the top that will go around bike handlebars. 
Features an adjustable cotton shoulder strap that would make it perfect for a 
backpack or purse. 

A bike bag, a shoulder bag, a farmer's market bag, a handy sack, 
the list goes on. A large fanny back if you hook the leather straps through a belt.

The outside is vinyl and the inside is a heavy canvas with 
heavy leather strapping and a cotton twill shoulder strap. 

In good condition but features a few vintage flaws that add to the
style. 

Dimensions:
10"w x 12"l x 4"d


*These are 30-40 year old vintage items and do have minor 
imperfections.
